				"title": "<a class=\"index\" id=\"93814\"></a>Poängbedömning enligt MADRS",
				"text": "<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p>F&ouml;ljande regler brukar anges f&ouml;r po&auml;ng&shy;bed&ouml;mning enligt MADRS med 10 fr&aring;gor: <br /><br /></p>\r\n<br style=\"font-weight: bold;\" />\r\n<table>\r\n<tbody>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td><strong>Po&auml;ng</strong></td>\r\n<td><strong>Bed&ouml;mning</strong></td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&lt; 10</td>\r\n<td>Inneb&auml;r oftast att inga aktuella <br />depressionssymtom finns</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>15&ndash;20</td>\r\n<td>Lindriga depressionssymtom</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>\r\n<p></p>\r\n<p>21&ndash;30</p>\r\n</td>\r\n<td>M&aring;ttliga, men kliniskt tydliga depressionssymtom</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&gt; 30</td>\r\n<td>Sv&aring;ra depressionssymtom</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n<tr>\r\n<td>&gt; 40</td>\r\n<td>Inneb&auml;r ofta s&aring; sv&aring;ra symtom att inl&auml;ggning p&aring; psykiatrisk klinik &auml;r aktuell</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n</td>\r\n</tr>\r\n</tbody>\r\n</table>",
